    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a third person adventure game in open world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the Story of Seppo with movie style cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes you to Finland 1994.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action packed Open World game with some RPG-Elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stats you can upgrade  (HP, XP, Levels, Power, Speed, Stamina, drunkennes, money, inventory, cars) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight mode like fighting games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy and drive cars, ride bikes, work, Drink...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crazy story is inspired by life and true locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day cycle and clock that affects shops etc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather system.</p>",
